Description:
CHISEL OUT YOUR FUTURE IN CHISWICK!
"Still shopping around for that perfect Christmas present. 20 Chiswick Street is it - the wife will love you forever."
Firstly, congratulations on being one of the first people to view this listing. With many buyers putting their search for a home on pause this week, you can avoid the dreaded "multiple offer scenario". In fact, if you get in early enough you might be able to secure your dream this side of the new year.
Undoubtably Timbertop is Cardinia Shire's premier estate. With commanding views and a prominent north-side position, the local residents are proud to call Chiswick Street their home.
The expansive house is perfect for the family upgrade, featuring:
- Four bedrooms, plus a designated study;
- Theatre room and rumpus room;
- Open plan living/dining area;
- The largest kitchen you're likely to see with elevated stone bench tops and butler's pantry;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car garage;
- Good size backyard.
Merry Christmas, happy house hunting.
